SELECT 
  frpm.count AS 'Free Meal Count (K-12)',
  enrollment.k12 AS 'Enrollment (K-12)',
  ROUND(frpm.count / enrollment.k12, 2) AS 'Eligible Free Rate (K-12)'
FROM 
  frpm
  JOIN schools ON frpm.cdscode = schools.cdscode
WHERE 
  schools.county_code = '011'
  AND frpm.low_grade = 'K-12'
ORDER BY 
  'Eligible Free Rate (K-12)' DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  frpm.count AS frpm_count, 
  ROUND(frpm.count / enrollment.count, 4) AS eligible_free_rate
FROM 
  california_schools.frpm 
  INNER JOIN 
    california_schools.schools 
  ON 
    frpm.cdscode = schools.cdscode 
WHERE 
  schools.statustype = 'Continuation' 
  AND frpm.count > 0 
  AND enrollment.count > 0 
ORDER BY 
  eligible_free_rate 
LIMIT 
  3

SELECT s.zip
FROM schools s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cdscode = f.cdscode
WHERE f.charter_school = '1' AND s.county = 'Fresno'

SELECT 
  s.street, 
  s.streetabr, 
  s.city, 
  s.zip, 
  s.state, 
  COUNT(f.frpm_count) AS frpm_count
FROM 
  schools s
  LEFT JOIN frpm f ON s.cdscode = f.cdscode
WHERE 
  f.frpm_count > 0
GROUP BY 
  s.street, 
  s.streetabr, 
  s.city, 
  s.zip, 
  s.state
ORDER BY 
  frpm_count DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT s.phone
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f.cdscode = s.cdscode
WHERE f.charter_school = '1' AND s.opendate > '2000-01-01'

JOIN satscores sc ON s.cdscode = sc.cds

    3

JOIN schools s ON sats.cds = s.cdscode

    s.school, 
    s.street, 
    s.streetabr, 
    s.city, 
    s.zip, 
    s.state, 
    frpm.enrollment_k12 - frpm.enrollment_ages517 AS diff
FROM 
    california_schools.frpm AS frpm
JOIN 
    california_schools.schools AS s
ON 
    frpm.cdscode = s.cdscode
WHERE 
    frpm.enrollment_k12 - frpm.enrollment_ages517 > 30

SELECT 
  sname, 
  dname, 
  cname, 
  (frpm_count / enrollment) * 100 AS percent_eligible_free_meals
FROM 
  california_schools.frpm
  JOIN california_schools.satscores
  ON frpm.cdscode = satscores.cds
WHERE 
  (frpm_count / enrollment) * 100 > 0.1 
  AND satscores.avgscrread >= 1500
ORDER BY 
  percent_eligible_free_meals DESC

SELECT s.fundingtype
FROM schools s
JOIN satscores sc ON s.cdscode = sc.cds
WHERE sc.avgscrmath > 400 AND s.county = 'Riverside'
GROUP BY s.fundingtype

    s.city,
    s.zip,
    s.state
FROM 
    california_schools.frpm AS frpm
    JOIN california_schools.schools AS s ON frpm.cds_code = s.cds_code

    frpm.county_code = '06037'

  sname, 
  avgscrwrite, 
  phone

  satscores

    schools

    satscores.cds = schools.cdscode 
WHERE 
  schools.opendate > '1991-01-01'

  schools.closeddate < '2000-01-01'

  sname, 
  avgscrwrite,

FROM schools s

  WHERE f.district_type = 'Locally Funded'
)

SELECT 
    s.opendate 
FROM 
    schools s 
WHERE 
    s.statustype = 'Public' 
    AND s.grade_level = 'K-12' 
    AND s.enrollment = (SELECT MAX(enrollment) FROM schools s2 WHERE s2.statustype = 'Public' AND s2.grade_level = 'K-12')

    s.city, 
    COUNT(s.cdscod) AS enrollment
FROM 
    california_schools.satscores s
WHERE 
    s.enroll12 > 0
GROUP BY 
    s.city
ORDER BY 
    enrollment ASC
LIMIT 5

    s.cdscode, 
    s.school, 
    COUNT(f.enrollment) AS enrollment
  FROM 
    schools s
  JOIN 
    frpm f ON s.cdscode = f.cdscode
  WHERE 
    f.low_grade = '1' AND f.high_grade = '12'
  GROUP BY

SELECT 
  e.cdscode, 
  e.school, 
  f.percent_free_meal_count_k_12 / f.enrollment_k_12 AS eligible_free_rate
FROM 
  enrollment_rank e
  JOIN 
  frpm f ON e.cdscode = f.cdscode
WHERE 
  e.cdscode IN (SELECT cdscode FROM enrollment_rank ORDER BY enrollment DESC OFFSET 9 ROWS FETCH NEXT 2 ROWS ONLY)
ORDER BY 
  eligible_free_rate

  s.name AS school_name,
  ROUND(FRPM_COUNT.K12 / ENROLLMENT.K12, 2) AS eligible_free_reduced_price_meal_rate
FROM 
  california_schools.frpm FRPM_COUNT
  INNER JOIN california_schools.schools S ON FRPM_COUNT.cdscode = S.cdscode
WHERE 
  S.edopscode = '66'
  AND FRPM_COUNT.k12 > 0
ORDER BY 
  FRPM_COUNT.k12 DESC
LIMIT 5

FROM california_schools.frpm AS frpm
JOIN california_schools.schools AS s ON frpm.cdscode = s.cdscode

FROM satscores
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.cdscode

FROM schools

WHERE district = 'Fresno Unified'
ORDER BY avgscrread ASC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  s.name, 
  s.county, 
  AVG(s.avgscrread) AS avg_reading_score
FROM 
  satscores s
  JOIN schools sch ON s.cds = sch.cdscode
WHERE 
  s.rtype = 'F'  -- Exclusively virtual
  AND sch.charter = 'Y'  -- Virtual school
  AND s.enroll12 > 0  -- Not empty school
GROUP BY 
  s.county, 
  s.name
ORDER BY 
  AVG(s.avgscrread) DESC
LIMIT 5

  s.sname, 
  s.dname, 
  s.cname, 
  ss.avgscrmath
FROM 
  schools s 
  JOIN satscores ss ON s.cdscode = ss.cds
ORDER BY 
  ss.avgscrmath DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
    s.name, 
    s.county, 
    AVG(s.AvgScrMath + s.AvgScrRead + s.AvgScrWrite) AS average_score
FROM 
    satscores s
JOIN 
    schools s2 ON s.cds = s2.cdscode
ORDER BY 
    average_score ASC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
    s.sname, 
    s.city, 
    AVG(s.avgscrwrit) AS avg_writing_score
FROM 
    satscores s
JOIN 
    schools sch ON s.cds = sch.cdscode
WHERE 
    s.numge1500 > 0
GROUP BY 
    s.sname, s.city
ORDER BY 
    COUNT(s.numtsttakr) DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  s.name, 
  AVG(satscores.avgscrwrit) AS avg_writing_score
FROM 
  schools s
  JOIN satscores ON s.cdscode = satscores.cds
  JOIN frpm ON s.cdscode = frpm.cdscode

  s.statustype = 'Active' 
  AND s.charter = 'N'

  AND sadmfname1 = 'Ricci'

ORDER BY 
  avg_writing_score DESC

    COUNT(f.cdscode) AS enrollment_count

    schools s

    frpm f ON s.cdscode = f.cdscode

    s.statustype = 31

    s.school_name

    COUNT(DISTINCT s.cdscode) AS monthly_average_number_of_schools

    schools s

    s.county = 'Alameda'
    AND s.statustype = 'Elementary School District'
    AND s.opendate >= '1980-01-01'
    AND s.opendate < '1981-01-01'

  COUNT(DISTINCT s2.cdscode) AS merged_elementary_sds

  schools s1

  s.county, 
  COUNT(s.school) AS total_closures

    s.school_name, 
    frpm.percent_eligible_frpm_ages_517 AS percent_eligible_frpm_ages_517
FROM 
    california_schools.frpm

    frpm.county_name = 'Los Angeles'

  COUNT(s.school_name) AS num_schools, 
  COUNT(DISTINCT s.low_grade) AS num_grade_spans
FROM 
  california_schools.frpm s
WHERE 
  s.county_name = 'Adelanto'

  s.school_name
ORDER BY 
  num_grade_spans DESC

SELECT 
    c.name AS county_name, 
    COUNT(s.cdscode) AS num_schools
FROM 
    schools s 
JOIN 
    frpm f ON s.cdscode = f.cdscode

    f.virtual = 'F' 
    AND s.county IN (SELECT county FROM schools WHERE city IN ('San Diego', 'Santa Barbara'))

    c.name

    num_schools DESC

SELECT 
  s.school, 
  s.latitude, 
  s.school_type
FROM 
  schools s
ORDER BY 
  s.latitude DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  s.city, 
  s.school, 
  s.low_grade

  schools s

  s.state = 'CA'

  AND s.low_grade IS NOT NULL 
  AND s.low_grade!= '' 
ORDER BY 
  s.low_grade

SELECT 
    gsoffered
FROM 
    schools
WHERE 
    latitude = (SELECT MAX(longitude) FROM schools)

  s.city, 
  COUNT(s.school) AS num_schools, 
  COUNT(DISTINCT s.cdscode) AS num_unique_schools

  schools s

    COUNT(*) as count,

    schools

    admfname1,

    count DESC

     COUNT(CASE WHEN gender IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)) AS 'Percentage of Male Clients'

SELECT 
    (t2.balance - t1.balance) / t1.balance * 100 AS increase_rate
FROM 
    (SELECT 
         account_id, 
         balance, 
         DATE_FORMAT(date, '%Y/%m/%d') AS date
     FROM 
         trans
     WHERE 
         account_id IN (SELECT 
                          account_id 
                         FROM 
                          loan 
                         WHERE 
                          DATE(date) = '1993-07-05' 
                         AND status = 'APPROVED' 
                         ORDER BY 
                          date LIMIT 1) 
     AND DATE(date) BETWEEN '1993-03-22' AND '1998-12-27') AS t1
JOIN 
    (SELECT 
         account_id, 
         balance, 
         DATE_FORMAT(date, '%Y/%m/%d') AS date
     FROM 
         trans
     WHERE 
         account_id IN (SELECT 
                          account_id 
                         FROM 
                          loan 
                         WHERE 
                          DATE(date) = '1993-07-05' 
                         AND status = 'APPROVED' 
                         ORDER BY 
                          date LIMIT 1) 
     AND DATE(date) BETWEEN '1993-03-22'
